    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Strategy:<br />
<br />
The strategy is quiet simpel. You set up your fellowship as fast as possible. Burn twice, first Forest Guardian, second Jarsmind. Then you should have all important Comps and Condition/Follower in game.<br />
Your fellowship&#39;s task is to go second and controll the sitepath. <br />
<br />
<br />
Your Shadow should adds some burden with the site (courtyard parapet), also good to cycle, and with Porter Troll.<br />
If you can spot two burdens and some deomarlized, play neekersbreecers bog. so you get some additional twillight pool. replace the two keysite with Unforgiving Depths or Traveled Leader. <br />
Your hordes will supplie you with enough minions. so at site 6 it should be possible to rush your enemy. With your Keyward u can add again additional Pool so  it should be easy to play 3 or 4 trolls. Chose him to move again and again you can play 2 - 4 trolls. <br />
